These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
City: miami, san-francisco, colone, london
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, gospel
1. the person traveling to colone is between the fan of funk and the fan of d&b##2
2. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
3. the fan of funk is not to the left of the fan of funk##8
4. the fan of d&b is not the person traveling to colone##6
5. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to miami##5
6. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| City   | london  | miami | colone | san-francisco  |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | funk   | gospel  | d&b |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, rat, mouse, ferret
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, russian, indonesian, british
1. the british is not to the left of the british##8
2. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the snake is the russian##1
4. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the snake and the owner of the rat##2
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the owner of the mouse and the indian##7
6. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
7. the indian is not to the left of the indian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Pet   | mouse | rat          | ferret | snake     |
| Nationality    | indonesian      | british | indian | russian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
House: modern, colonial, victorian, gothic-revival
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, canadian, malaysian, japanese
1. the spanish is not to the left of the victorian house##8
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the colonial house is on the right of the modern house##1
4. the colonial house is in an even position##4
5. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
6. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
7. the gothic-revival house is the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| House           | modern | colonial | victorian     | gothic-revival |
| Nationality   | canadian    | japanese   | spanish | malaysian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, monopoly, go, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific, comedy, western
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is not to the left of the person watching scientific movies##8
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing scrabble is not to the right of the person watching comedy movies##8
5. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
7. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | go   | monopoly         | scrabble   | mah-jongg    |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | western | comedy | zombie |

