.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, rat, horse
There 4 different types of food: spinach, cabbage, strawberry, zucchini
1. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the lizard##7
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person eating strawberry##5
3. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the owner of the frog##7
4. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person eating zucchini##8
5. the person eating zucchini is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the person eating cabbage##7
6. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the owner of the horse##5
7. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
8. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | lizard   | rat | horse | frog    |
| Food         | spinach | zucchini   | strawberry   | cabbage |

