.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, argentine, thai, indonesian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, august, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
3. the thai is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
5. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
6. the indonesian is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
7. the indonesian is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality          | indonesian | mexican | argentine  | thai |
| Birthday   | june   | april         | august | december |

