.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
House: cottage, palace, craftsman, art-deco
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, emerald, pink, amber
1. the person who likes emerald is not to the left of the palace house##8
2. the person who likes amber is somewhere between the art-deco house and the person who likes pink##7
3. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the right of the person who likes blood-red##5
4. the person who likes amber is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
5. the person who likes amber is not to the left of the palace house##8
6. the cottage house is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
8. the cottage house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| House   | palace      | craftsman | cottage | art-deco   |
| Color      | blood-red | pink | amber  | emerald |

