.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, dancing, fishing, card-games
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, blood-red, emerald, light-blue
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person who likes light-blue##8
2. the person who likes light-blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes emerald is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##8
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who's hobby is fishing##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Hobby     | dancing | fishing | card-games | video-games     |
| Color   | orange   | emerald        | light-blue          | blood-red |

