.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, june, september
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, electrician, engineer, architect
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in september and the entrepreneur##2
2. the architect is on the far left##1
3. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
5. the electrician is the electrician##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is not the engineer##6
7. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##8
8. the entrepreneur is not to the left of the electrician##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday   | september   | december | june | july |
| Job     | architect | electrician       | entrepreneur  | engineer    |

