.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, sprite, coffee, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, volleyball, weightlifting
1. the person drinking cola is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
2. the person who's sport is swimming is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
4. the person drinking coffee is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
6. the person who's sport is rugby is not to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | coffee | soy-milk      | cola   | sprite  |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | rugby | swimming | volleyball |

