.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, singing, dancing, gardening
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, august, june
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
4. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##8
5. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##8
6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | camping     | gardening | dancing | singing |
| Birthday     | august | june  | march    | february   |

