.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
City: edinburgh, hannover, san-francisco, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, satire, horror, martial-arts
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is not to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##8
2. the person watching action movies is not to the right of the person traveling to hannover##8
3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to new-york##5
4. the person watching action movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the person watching horror movies##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City    | hannover        | new-york | san-francisco      | edinburgh    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | horror   | satire | martial-arts |

