.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, manager, social-worker, writer
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, rock-climbing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##8
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the right of the electrician##8
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the manager##1
4. the electrician is on the far left or far right##3
5. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the manager##7
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the manager##3
8. the writer is on the left or right of the manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Job   | writer | manager         | social-worker    | electrician       |
| Hobby      | gardening | woodworking | traveling | rock-climbing |

