The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, december, january, february
1. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
2. the fan of trance is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the fan of trance##5
4. the fan of d&b is between the fan of trance and the person who's birthday is in january##2
5. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Music-Genre   | punk     | d&b | trance        | hip-hop       |
| Birthday      | january | december  | august | february |

