.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, oliveros, havana, dunhill
House: modern, cottage, palace, tower
 1. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
 2. the dunhill-smoker is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
 3. the cain-smoker is the palace house##1
 4. the palace house is not to the right of the cottage house##8
 5. the tower house is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 6. the cottage house is somewhere to the right of the havana-smoker##5
 7. the cottage house is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the cain-smoker is not to the right of the palace house##8
 9. the cottage house is not to the left of the cain-smoker##8
10. the oliveros-smoker is not to the left of the modern house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Cigar          | oliveros    | havana | cain | dunhill |
| House   | modern | tower  | palace     | cottage    |

