.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-16::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, hedgehog, horse, cat
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, skateboard, jet-ski
1. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5
2. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
3. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person driving the airplane##5
4. the person driving the skateboard is the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3     |    4    |
| Pet    | horse   | hedgehog    | cat   | rat |
| Transport   | airplane | skateboard | jet-ski | motorbike |

