.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, zinnia, daffodil, azalea
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, cooking, filmmaking
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who growszinnia##8
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
4. the person who growsdaffodil is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
5. the person who growsazalea is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
8. the person who growsdaffodil is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Flower           | daffodil | azalea | zinnia | poppy   |
| Hobby   | cooking       | filmmaking      | magic-tricks    | chess |

