.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, mouse, lizard, hedgehog
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, april, august, november
1. the owner of the lizard is the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the hedgehog##2
7. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Pet    | hedgehog        | mouse | goat | lizard |
| Birthday   | november | august | april   | may    |

