.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo, soccer, cycling
The people have 4 different jobs:  dressmaker, social-worker, electrician, security-guard
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not the electrician##6
2. the electrician is not to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##8
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is cycling##7
4. the social-worker is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
5. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the security-guard##5
6. the dressmaker is not to the right of the social-worker##8
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the security-guard##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | cycling | water-polo  | soccer  |
| Job   | dressmaker | social-worker   | security-guard | electrician |

