.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, mango, peach, orange
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, chess, singing, baking
1. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person eating tomato##6
2. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person eating orange is not to the left of the person who's hobby is baking##8
4. the person eating peach is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
5. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is gardening##7
6. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person eating peach##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food         | mango    | orange | tomato | peach |
| Hobby   | chess | baking      | singing     | gardening     |

 